{"tid":1255844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又殺到埋身] 區議會選舉指引要求候選人簽擁護基本法確認書","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T10:31:41.000Z","uid":230609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa098c69d07578a21afc4ad9502ce6c9182ffc4","tid":1255844,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"選管會就住嚟緊嘅區議會修訂左新嘅選舉指引<br />\n入面新增左要參選人聲明擁護基本法/擁護香港不可分離 <br />\n以及選舉主任全權決定提名有冇效嘅修訂<br />\n換言之 即係之前DQ立法會議員嘅規則<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MT7KaM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MT7KaM.jpg&h=a53f80d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家選管會進行緊公眾諮詢(11/6-10/7)<br />\n<strong>聽日(25/6) 就已經係公眾諮詢大會啦</strong><br />\n時間地點係7-9 p.m.鰂魚涌社區會堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/24/P2019062400670.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F24%2FP2019062400670.htm&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=6698f4df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/24/P2019062400670.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n儲氣等緊626嘅人 都可以send email(eacenq@eac.hk)<br />\n或者寄信(香港灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓選管會秘書處)"},{"pid":"4921be5e133517d3642ba60ec79914bd50906215","tid":1255844,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:40:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dcebb0156b3c987539ca2c33cebe70af7814b53","tid":1255844,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"連登街站團！<br />\n公海link: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期戰就係要落地開花，令議題喺各地保持熱度，大家幫到既盡幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b87db93d312864060d9c6b80e053947e1f46f97","tid":1255844,"uid":54303,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"屌個制度真心on9<br />\n係咪想個個連登仔都走去扮建制派𠝹鳩你票先安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\"